import matplotlib.pyplot as plt, mpld3
mpld3.enable_notebook()

plt.plot([3,1,4,1,5], 'ks-', mec='w', mew=5, ms=20)
plt.imshow(np.random.rand(10, 10, 3))
mpld3.display()
